  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 19-70,

          -  Schizophrenia or Schizoaffective disorder

          -  stabilized but not expecting to be discharged soon

          -  capacity to give informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  acutely psychotic

          -  acutely medically ill

          -  renal insufficiency

          -  hypercalcemia

          -  hyperparathyroidism
      </textblock>
